  <brief_title>Bimatoprost Monotherapy vs. Dual Therapy With Travoprost and Timolol in Patients With Glaucoma and Ocular Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Bimatoprost 0.03% Monotherapy vs. Dual Therapy With Travoprost 0.004% and Timolol 0.5% in Patients With Glaucoma and Ocular Hypertension</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
