  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluate the IOP-lowering efficacy and quality of life in patients using bimatoprost 0.03%
      monotherapy versus dual therapy with travoprost 0.004% and timolol 0.5% for the treatment of
      glaucoma or ocular hypertension.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
